# Live Verification and Matt Handoff

## Step

Assert the finish line in production, behaviorally — live remainders block:

1. Admin mints a token over the prod API.
2. That token reads an unpublished post.
3. A write attempt with it returns 403.
4. Axiom shows both as structured auth events.
5. Open a **tidy issue on `mattpocock/course-video-manager`** (Joel, 2026-07-17) carrying the full agentic context: what agent tokens are, the discovery URL, mint/revoke flow, `content:read` semantics and exclusions, plus an inline ready-to-paste `SKILL.md` body so his agent can adopt it with one Write. Recon facts: we have push access; his repo already consumes the AI Hero API via `app/services/ai-hero-auth-service.ts` (Effect, OAuth device flow) and documents it via the `document-ai-hero-api` skill (which reads ai-hero *source* from a local clone — the issue should pitch the discovery surface as the replacement for that folklore); docs live in `docs/ai-hero-api.md`. Issue only after assertions 1-4 hold (never hand Matt a prompt against an unverified surface). A code PR is fallback-only if Matt asks — his Effect conventions are his agents' to apply.
6. Reply in Matt's Slack thread (https://eggheadio.slack.com/archives/C0211NSK3TP/p1784281556387689) with a **paste-able agent prompt** + the issue link — one URL + his admin PAT and the agent self-onboards from the discovery surface (Joel, 2026-07-17: no hand-holding breakdown). Matt confirms his agent works. Then ✅ react on the thread root (`jc-slack react '<permalink>' --emoji white_check_mark`).

Resolved when all six held, receipts (curl transcripts redacted of token material, Axiom query + result, issue URL, Slack permalink) are linked in the Result, and the brief flips to done.

## Receipts so far (2026-07-17, assertions 1-4 GREEN)

Verified against production `https://www.aihero.dev` (deploy `ai-hero-jjg7dcvou`, main @ `a3bd5a8`), script `live-verify.mjs` (receipts-only output, no token material):

1. **Mint over API**: 201, `tokenPrefix=aih_pat_059c71ab…`, scopes `["content:read"]`, raw token shape valid, minted with a 1-day-old admin device token.
2. **Privileged read**: GET `/api/posts?slugOrId=post_3a7fw` → 200, `state=draft`. Anonymous control on the same id → 401.
3. **Write denied**: PUT `/api/posts` with the PAT → 403 with `docs: /api` in the body.
4. **Axiom**: 3 structured `auth.personal-access-token.verify` events in the `vercel` dataset at 17:41Z matching the run (info/accepted GET, info PUT, warn read-after-revoke) with requestId, path, method, tokenKind.
5. Lifecycle bonus: DELETE revoke → 200; read-after-revoke → 401.
6. Discovery: `/api` teaches agent tokens; `openapi.json` serves OpenAPI 3.1 with `securitySchemes`.

Remaining: issue on course-video-manager ([draft](./matt-issue-draft.svx) pending Joel's go), Slack reply with agent prompt, Matt confirmation, ✅ react.
